感到非常生气”。</p><p>马来西亚政府<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/malaysian-gigs-to-have-mandatory-kill-switch-after-the-1975-gay-kiss-controversy-3530488">宣布，音乐会组织者现在必须有一个“终止开关”</a> ，以阻止违反指导方针的表演。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-1975-share-at-their-very-best-live-album-and-announce-vinyl-edition-3532915">The 1975 分享“At Their Very Best”现场专辑并宣布黑胶版的帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
